This is the readme file for the Game of Life - Gosu project.

Running
=======

You need to install the gosu gem first:
$ gem install gosu

Run the main.rb file to start the application:
$ ruby main.rb

Controls
========

  Key    |       Action
---------+----------------------
  <A>    | Toggle auto-mode
<Space>  | Simulate the next round
<Return> | Repopulate the field
<Escape> | Quit the application

Colors
======

Green => This cell is alive.
Blue  => This cell was revived.
White => This cell is dead.
